name: Metamorph
description:
Waited too long to crossing out the white canvas.
Since NFT world has born, now many artist can show and express their passion of making arts. It was so difficult to keep artist career before NFT world has born, lack of money, appreciation and chance.
Like caterpillar has waited to become beautiful butterfly, time has its own metamorph giving many artists the chance to crossing out the colors on their canvas. 

Size: 2100x1800 px
Digital art only.
